## <a id="limitations"></a>Limitations

When using <%= vars.product_short %> with more than 2000 service instances per foundation we recommend enabling the <%= vars.product_short%> cache, see [Enable <%= vars.product_short %> Cache](installing.html/#enable-cache).
Enabling the <%= vars.product_short%> will reduce the impact on the performance of <%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %> due to requests made to the Cloud Controller.

